    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Is that because magic functions can be customized within individual profiles that won't be compatible on other users systems and you all don't want code that won't work on anyone else's system to propagate the web?\nIt is very convenient as a user to save your use of magic functions and bash commands to a script to run over and over. Is there a better way to use the full ipython functionality in a script besides this?\n"
